msg: A patch from Sascha Rodekamp "Color of links in retrieved list for Tomahawk theme" (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-3527) - OFBIZ-3527
In Tomahawk theme the links in the retrieved list are not following the theme colors.
I have also found that it's not exactly the same problem depending on the place the lookup is used (or maybe how it's used). This commit does not fix them all but make things better and usable.
